<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْقُرْآنُ هَيِّنٌ، الْوَحْيُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> أَشَدُّ .»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
